snippet.textDisplay: Magical, mesmerising, mind blowing, stunning, I am speechless and short of words. This song will cross 100M mark in few weeks. The magical journey of Star Shah was so captivating, bless you brother. And he rightly pointed out that addition of Zeeshan’s melodious voice added not 4 Chand but 8 Chand. Zulfi is a musical genius and lots of credit to him for discovering such artists and the whole CS team for creating such a masterpiece. The set was amazing and ans I must say it’s simply splendid to see such attention to detail.
